'''Separation anxiety disorder''' is a psychological issue in which somebody experiences very intense [[anxiety]] when being seprated from other people or their homes, [[school]] or friends to whom the person carries a strong emotional connection. There is excess fear or worry which is atypical of the true mental age and level. This condition may sometimes create physical troubles. Those under 18 are at highest risk for the problem.
